gurmukhi: ਕਾਲਖ ਬਿਹੰਡਣ ਕਿਲਵਿਖ ਹਰਣ ਸੁਰ ਨਰ ਮੁਨਿ ਬੰਦਤ ਚਰਨ ||
transliteration: Kaalakh Bihanndan Kilvikh Haran Sur Nar Mounndi) Bandat Charan||
translation: Remover of darkness and destroyer of sins, all the gods, men and sages bow at His Feet.

gurmukhi: ਖੰਡਣ ਅਖੰਡ ਮੰਡਣ ਅਭੈ ਨਮੋ ਨਾਥ ਭੳੁ ਭੈ ਹਰਨ ||੩||੩੪||
transliteration: Khanndan Akhannddmandan Abhai Namo Naath Bhau Bhai Haran||3||34||
translation: He is breaker of the unbreakable; He is the establisher on the Fearless position; Salutation to Thee, O Lord, the remover of fear.3.34.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ ਨਾਥ ਨ੍ਰਿਦਾੲਿਕ ਨਮੋ ਨਿਮ ਰੂਪ ਨਿਰੰਜਨ ||
transliteration: Namo Naath Nridaaik Namo Nim Roop Niranjan||
translation: Salutation to Him the Merciful Donor Lord! Salutation to Him, the Transcendent and Modest Lord!
The Destroyer of Indestructible, Invincible, Indiscriminate and Imperishable Lord.

gurmukhi: ਅਛੈ ਅਖੈ ਅਬਿਕਾਰ ਅਭੈ ਅਨਭਿੱਜ ਅਭੇਦਨ ||
transliteration: Achhai Akhai Abikaar Abhai Anbhijj Abhedan||
translation: Inassailable, Incorruptible, Devoid of vices, Fearless, unattached and Undistinguishable Lord.
Affliction of the Unafflicted, Blissful without blemish and the Unassailable.

gurmukhi: ਅਾਜਾਨ ਬਾਹੁ ਸਾਰੰਗਧਰ ਖੜਗ ਪਾਣ ਦੁਰਜਨ ਦਲਨ ||
transliteration: Aajaan Baah(u) Saarandhar Khadag Paan Durjan Dalan||
translation: The Lord with long arms upto knees, wearer of the bow and the sword for vanquishing the enemies.

gurmukhi: ਨਰ ਵਰ ਨਰੇਸ ਨਾੲਿਕ ਨ੍ਰਿਪਣਿ ਨਮੋ ਨਵਲ ਜਲ ਥਲ ਰਵਣ ||੪||੩੫||
transliteration: Nar Var Dares Naaik Nripan(i) Namo Naval Jal Thal Ravan||4||35||
translation: The Sovereign of good people, hero and Master of armies; Salutation to Him who Pervades water and lands.4.35.

gurmukhi: ਦੀਨ ਦਯਾਲ ਦੁਖ ਹਰਨ ਦੁਰਮਤ ਹੰਤਾ ਦੁਖ ਖੰਡਣ ||
transliteration: Deen Dayaal Doukh Haran Durmat Hantaa Doukh Khanndan||
translation: He is the Merciful Lord of the lowly, destroyer of suffering, and vicious intellect and the refuter of suffering.

gurmukhi: ਮਹਾਂ ਮੋਨ ਮਨ ਹਰਨ ਮਦਨ ਮੂਰਤ ਮਹਿ ਮੰਡਨ ||
transliteration: Mahaan Mon Man Haran Madan Moondat Maih Mandan||
translation: He is greatly peaceful, captivator of the heart, alluring like Cupid and Creator of the world.

gurmukhi: ਅਮਿਤ ਤੇਜ ਅਬਿਕਾਰ ਅਖੈ ਅਾਭੰਜ ਅਮਿਤ ਬਲ ||
transliteration: Amit Tej Abikaar Akhai Aabhanj Amit Bal||
translation: He is the Lord of Limitless Glory, without vices, indestructible, Invincible having Boundless Power.

gurmukhi: ਨਿਰਭੰਜ ਨਿਰਭੳੁ ਨਿਰਵੈਰ ਨਿਰਜੁਰ ਨ੍ਰਿਪ ਜਲ ਥਲ ||
transliteration: Nirbhanj Nirbhau Birvair Birjur Nrip Jal Thal||
translation: He is Unbreakable, without fear and enmity, without malice and the monarch of waters and lands.

gurmukhi: ਅੱਛੈ ਸਰੂਪ ਅੱਛੂ ਅਛਿਤ ਅਛੈ ਅਛਾਨ ਅਛਰ ||
transliteration: Achchhai Saroopachchhodh Achhit Achhai Achhaad Achhar||
translation: He is unassailable Entity, Untouchable, Eternal, Imperishable, Unhidden and without deception.
